Description:
SOLD! ANOTHER AVAILABLE – INQUIRE WITHIN
This property caters for your toddlers to have the space to play outside on this spacious terrace and for those adorable pet’s.
Looking for convenience at your doorstep in a quiet environment with plenty of space to live? Look no further as this two bedroom apartment located in The Magnificent Mosaic has it all! This low rise building is highly sought after, once you see it you’ll also understand why. The open plan living area incorporates dining and living & an adjoining gourmet kitchen. With public transport at your feet, a short stroll from Etihad Stadium and all that Docklands and CBD offers, this is an opportunity that seldom comes around and is ready to move in now !
Reasons why you will buy this apartment:
• Generous size terrace with secured gate access to the park across the road
• Spacious open plan kitchen and living space
• East facing with park views
• Car space with storage cage
• Stainless steel kitchen appliances and stone benchtops
• Close to free public transport, restaurants and cafes
• Heating and cooling split system
• European Laundry
Inspections welcomed, for further information please feel free to contact me or call at any time of the day.

Lyle Dean 0417 343 541

Description:
Wonderful Harbour Views, Great Location! Great Value
Nestled in the “Harbour 1” complex located in the NewQuay waterfront development, and moments from the waters edge is this cosy two bedroom apartment available for sale and would be ideal for the first home owner or the savvy investor.
Features of this apartment include:
- Spacious open plan living area with floor to ceiling windows of views to the water
- Gourmet kitchen features granite benches with long island bench with 'breakfast bar'
- Stainless steel appliances
- Ducted heating and cooling
- Balcony with unchangeable water views of the harbour
- Secure undercover car space
- Access to Residents gym, media room, and luxury library room
On top of all this, the apartment is in a perfect location being in the vibrant NewQuay precinct, with the waterfront restaurant strip and Harbourtown shopping at your front door. A short tram ride within the free tram zone will have you in the centre of the CBD, universities, medical institutions and entertainment venues.
Don't wait any longer, call Peter Doan on 0423 399 999 to inspect now.

Description:
Stylish, Great CBD Views and low maintenance living in the coveted Quays development
This 13th floor gem is sure to come under the radar of city professionals, first home buyers, and smart investors looking for terrific returns. The complex is also one of the most desired in the Docklands and offers facilities which include a Health Club with a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio. Work, relax or study in The Resident’s Club on Level One which has a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, or entertain on the rooftop garden with tennis courts, BBQs and dining facilities.
You’ll love the spacious internal living spaces including the comfortable lounge and meals zone which offers floor-to-ceiling windows, quality timber flooring, and is adjoined by a stone-featured kitchen displaying a mirrored splashback and stainless steel appliances. The covered balcony (accessed via central living and bedroom) takes advantage of its position to offer breathtaking city views, while the bedroom also has CBD vistas as well as built-in robe storage. Other extras include a bathroom with European laundry, reverse cycle cooling, video intercom, and secure car space.
The surrounding NewQuay precinct offers an assortment of amazing restaurants, while you’re also close to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Costco, Medibank Icehouse, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel and Etihad stadium. With the free tram zone on your door step this apartment is the full package for low stress easy living.
Please call Clare Thompson on 0474 044 293 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Breathtaking Dual Aspect with Stunning Space
Showcasing an abundance of space on 145 sqm total (approx.) and splashed with graceful and sophisticated style befitting the coveted Conder residential complex, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment is utter bliss for those looking for space and style.
You’ll be lost for words when you step into the enormous central lounge and dining zone which has amazing floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for sensational natural light and views to the west, south, and the north. The balcony opens out from this generous main zone and offers a wonderful space to laze about on balmy Melbourne nights and enjoy meals and drinks.
The attractive stone kitchen has chic timber cabinetry, breakfast bar, and stainless steel Miele appliances. The sizeable master bedroom comes with its own private ensuite, while all three bedrooms have built-in robe storage and northern views. Other property highlights include a central bathroom, European laundry, central heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, storage cage, two secure car spaces, and access to the 25m indoor pool, gym, and outdoor grassed recreation area.
In a building by the award-winning Fender Katsalidis, enjoy the relaxed NewQuay Precinct where you can dine at superb nearby restaurants including The Conder restaurant, NewQuay International Buffet, Fish Bar, and Waterside Oriental Bistro. You’re also near Etihad Stadium, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, and Harbour Esplanade trams on your door step.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
Rare Townhouse Available in the Heart of Docklands
Located in the much sought after Victoria Harbour precinct of Docklands, this ultra-modern two storey townhouse captures all the appeal of the Docklands' lifestyle, immaculately presented and equally attractive to the owner-occupier and investor alike.
Consisting of 3 spacious bedrooms plus an extra study/guest bedroom, with 2 contemporary bathrooms plus 2 extra powder rooms along with 2 carparks and a storage cage to round things off, this rare gem is everything you desire right in the heart of Victoria Harbour.
Enjoy the spacious living and dining area which opens onto a courtyard and a generous balcony - overlooking the parkland - perfect for entertaining or just relaxing. The fully equipped kitchen features European style stainless steel appliances with stone benchtops and splash backs to continue the elegant theme.
The main bedroom with an ample walk-in-robe, leading into a full ensuite, will surely become your own retreat, whilst the other two generously sized bedrooms, all with their own individual cooling/heating share a stylish bathroom, designed with quality fittings and tiling lavishly extending from floor to ceiling.
Situated within easy walking distance to Southern Cross station, free trams, Safeway supermarket, banks and amenities, waterfront restaurants and cafes, the new Harbour Town and the CBD. You will be surprised by the peacefulness and quietness of its convenient location while being within minutes’ walk of all that you need.
Other features include European style laundry, 4 toilets, a/c - cooling/heating in every room, 2 balconies, a back courtyard, secure front and rear entrances, this complete package will not last long.

Description:
A North-Facing Docklands Stunner You Need To See
With an astonishing number of brilliant living highlights including wonderful open space, elegant contemporary style, and outstanding views to the north, this inspired two bedroom, two bathroom ‘Array’ apartment has your name written all over it!
Thoughtful attention to detail and a near flawless presentation are a couple of vital boxes ticked with this 13th floor gem. Expansive central living boasts excellent room for designated lounge and dining areas, with the adjoining tiled kitchen perfect with a well-designed breakfast bar with trendy shelving and premium stainless steel Miele appliances.
The balcony with a northerly orientation has plenty of space and offers fantastic views of the Yarra River and CBD buildings. The master bedroom is a great space to retire to at the end of the day and features direct access to the balcony along with dual built-in robes and an ensuite. Other property features include a luxury bathroom, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, and a secure car space. You also have access to an on-site gym as well as RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Make the most of all the terrific Yarra’s Edge attractions nearby which includes South Wharf with DFO shopping as well as great eateries and bars including Bangpop, Munich Brauhaus, and Common Man just to name a few. You’re also near Crown Entertainment Complex with world class restaurants, Capital City Trail, and public transport.

Description:
Stunning Townhouse Living in the New Quay Precinct
Spectacularly set over three luxury levels, and situated in the relaxed NewQuay Precinct just moments to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, this memorable 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhouse is inspired Docklands living.
A thoughtful design and exceptional attention to detail defines this outstanding urban oasis. The versatile floorplan has a great downstairs bedroom and stylish bathroom perfect for guests. Head up the stairs to the first floor and experience the bright and generous central lounge and dining hub as well as the gourmet kitchen complete with handy breakfast bar and stainless-steel gas appliances.
A balcony with treetop views feeds off from the living zone and delivers a tranquil space to enjoy summer BBQs and after work drinks. Two top floor bedrooms come with mirrored built-in robes including the main bedroom which also promises an ensuite, while the other bedroom has easy access to the immaculate main bathroom.
Other townhouse extras include a handy European laundry, polished timber floors, reverse cycle heating and cooling (including both upstairs beds), rainwater tank, and a double garage with bonus storage. Close to promenade restaurants, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and trams on Docklands Drive.

Description:
Townhouse Luxury Sets The Modern Standard
Buyers are in for a treat when they step inside this luxury 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhouse, which promises exquisite contemporary charisma while offering marvellous space and plenty of areas for alfresco entertaining.
Let’s start with the outside of this stellar two storey property, which boasts a spacious entertainer’s courtyard right at the front of the dwelling perfect for dinner parties and general unwinding. The rear of the townhouse also has a balcony adding even more outdoor versatility to your living experience.
Inside you can enjoy the vast living and dining zone which is serviced by a tranquil gas fireplace. The kitchen has everything you need including stone countertops, the right amount of storage, and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs you have both bedrooms each with their own impressive ensuites and built-in robes, a European laundry, and study area with integrated desk.
Other property features include a downstairs powder room, reverse cycle heating and cooling, storage cage, and two secure car spaces. This unique Wharf Street location has you right next to newly refurbished District Docklands with high end shops, new amenities and great dining destinations. With a continuation of District Docklands 150 million dollar upgrade these amenities will soon include a Hoyts Cinema complex, full-line supermarket and fresh food markets. Docklands Wharf is a stroll away which has an amazing selection of waterfront restaurants and water activities. You’re also within walking distance to Docklands planned new primary school, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the free tram zone for the 35, 70 and 86 trams, making access to the city a breeze.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive inspection.

Description:
Quays Luxury With Great Outdoor Entertaining
This stunning one bedroom apartment is sure to come under the radar of city professionals, first home buyers and smart investors looking for terrific consistent returns with the added bonus of a private terrace.
One of the undoubted highlights of this 7th-floor apartment is the large paved terrace accessed via the central living zone, which has a wealth of space as well as outstanding views. This area is sure to get a lot of use for meals, drinks, and general relaxing during the nicer spring and summer weather.
Inside, dazzling timber floors, bright floor-to-ceiling windows, stone benchtops, and premium fittings and fixtures will have you immediately enticed. The large lounge and dining zone offers easy access to the pristine kitchen which is complete with a trendy mosaic tiled splashback and stainless steel appliances. The comfortable bedroom with mirrored wardrobes has sliding doors allowing for an open or private living, while the bathroom is fitted with a handy concealed laundry.
Along with reverse cycle cooling, secure intercom, storage room, and secure car space, you also have access to a variety of amazing building facilities. These include a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, while there is a Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. Also, enjoy a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities. Take advantage of the option to buy fully furnished and expect a rent of $525 per week (as previous lease).
You’re further positioned in the NewQuay precinct which has easy access to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Medibank Icehouse, Costco, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Festival Hall, and the 35, 70, and 86 tram lines taking you all over Melbourne.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 for an exclusive viewing of this property.

Description:
Rare floor, oversized with full waterviews
Located in the highly renowned Conder building this stunning 2 bedroom apartment boasts endless panoramic views across the bay and the picturesque NewQuay Marina. Its extensive open-plan living and dining areas accommodate both casual entertaining and formal dining, with exclusive access out to your very own spacious entertainers’ balcony with uninterrupted and private views.
The ultra-spacious master bedroom features not only a study nook and views over the marina but also a glamorous walk in robe and simply stunning ensuite. The generously sized second bedroom also overlooking the Marina, is complemented by a second luxurious bathroom with a deep relaxing bath. Completed gracefully by your large designer kitchen with Miele appliances, it is sure to inspire your inner chef.
Enjoy the resort style facilities with the 25m indoor pool, gym and sauna or relax on the resident gardens. This opportunity also benefits from 2 secured car spaces and storage cage . Located in bubbling excitement of NewQuay you are amongst world class amenities of not only Docklands but also the Melbourne CBD, with public transport right on your doorstep.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Over 130sqm with unobstructed water and city views
If you’re not won over by the stunning city and waterfront views, then you will be enticed by the huge living space that comes with this converted two bedroom, two bathroom apartment on the 8th level of the Palladio complex.
Brilliant natural light fills up the large central living and separate dining zone which is serviced by the ultra-chic kitchen with quality s/steel appliances, while the relaxed private balcony is perfect for alfresco entertaining and is the ultimate spot to partake in the gorgeous views. The conversion from 3 bedrooms to 2 has allowed the extensive living area and separate dining area to make the most of the stunning views. Easily converted back to 3 bedrooms.
The master bedroom is an ideal retreat to retire to at the end of a long day with a walk-in robe and sleek ensuite, while the other bedroom comes with with BIRs, city views and a luxury bathroom are other internal highlights. Other benefits are separate laundry room, heating/cooling , intercom, 2 car spaces, storage cage and access to the pool, gym, and BBQ area.
Near promenade restaurants, The District Docklands Shopping Centre, Etihad Stadium, CBD attractions, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Affordable and luxurious with great bay views
Located on the 18th floor is this elegant two-bedroom apartment. It offers a spacious open plan kitchen and dinning area with spectacular views of Port Phillip Bay. Both bedrooms are generous in size and have built in robes. The kitchen is fitted with stainless steel Miele appliances with plenty of cupboard space and a stylish central bathroom.
The features of this apartment are the floor to ceiling double-glassed windows in both bedrooms, kitchen and dinning area that allows for natural light to flow in. Additional building features included secure car space with storage cage, intercom entry and a gym that will suit everyones fitness goals.
Its conveniently located on Lorimer Street which gives you easy access to Princess Highway, West Gate freeway, Etihad Stadium and with only a 10min drive to Port Melbourne beach. Within walking distance you have shops, cafs and waterfront restaurants.
This apartment will make an amazing opportunity for owner occupier or an investor

Description:
AMAZING OPPORTUNITY IN DOCKLANDS
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Etihad Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
This 2 bed, 1 bath, 1 car apartment, which has fantastic views of the Etihad Stadium, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathroom. A Euro-laundry and private balcony round out this well designed apartment.
Completing this apartment is split system heating/cooling, secure swipe/intercom entry, and a secure car space, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym. Whether you’re enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Etihad Stadium, this is low maintenance living without the price tag.
